Default Compiz Config:

Enable Enhanced Zoom Desktop
Zoom in Button Shift Super Button 4
Zoom out Button Shift Super Button 5

Enable Opacity Brightness and Saturation

Enable Desktop Cube.

Cube Cap Colors Transparent (slider all the way left) Top and Bottom
Skydome Choose Gradient Colors that will match the default Mint Theme
Transparent Cube Tab Opacity During Rotation set between 5 and 15.
Non Rotating Opacity set to Between 50 and 75

Rotate Cube
Zoom .5
Additional Settings Speed 4

3d Windows Enabled

Firepaint Enabled
Particle Settings:
Fire Particle Number 20000
FP Size 7
FP Slow down .5
FP Life .2

Disable Wobbly Windows Or at least speed them WAY up.

Enable Snapping Windows

This is just the bare minimum I do every time I configure Compiz.  I also set the desktop to be a solid black color.
Not sure if that can be done automatically when Compiz is enabled in the Desktop Settings Windows Menu.
